{
  "texts": [
    "To facilitate indepth research and improvements based on our work, the code is also open-sourced.",
    "This study shows that CircDA achieves higher accuracy than many state-of-theart methods on evaluation data from benchmark data.",
    "Case studies demonstrate that CircDA can effectively predict unknown disease associations.",
    "The applicability and robustness of CircDA are demonstrated.",
    "The frame diagram of CircDA is shown in Fig. 1."
  ]
}